Back To School Gift-away!

We are so excited about Back To School time, 📚✏✂️mostly because summer makes us super appreciative of teachers👩‍🏫 and routines🗓!   We also know that this time of year can be really hard on families when it comes to buying all those supplies needed, so we want to help 2 different families out!  It is out way of saying thank you for supporting and helping out our small business the rest of the year.    We are giving away 2 backpacks full of goodies for 1 preschooler and 1 early elementary kiddo!  
 
Entering is Easy!

✂️Like this post.

🖍Save this post (the little bookmark) and share it to your stories(the little paper airplane) tagging us @bannortoys!

✏Comment on the post what age backpack you would love to get for your family.

That’s it, do all the steps above to be entered!   We’ll choose 2 different winners for each of the backpacks on Wednesday 8/18(watch stories for the announcement), and mail the goodies out this week!   Must be in the USA to enter.
